<ab facs="#facs_241_r2l23"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> / . Der ıſt cʒü <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒeit niht anheim / Aber wenn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_241_r2l24">er her heim kümt / So <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir Jn darvmb <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> cʒe rede <expan>ſecʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_241_r2l25">ew ein <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> <expan>laſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> wiſſen / ob <expan>yema<ex>n</ex>t</expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>vvege<ex>n</ex></expan> cʒü vns kümt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_241_r2l26">vnd die <expan>vord<ex>er</ex>t</expan> / . wo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb vnd dinſt <expan>beweıſe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>möht<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_241_r2l27">Das <expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>allcʒ<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>vts<ex>upra</ex></expan> . </ab>
