<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Görg<ex>en</ex></expan> Schenken czü Geyrn </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan> her Görg, als ir uns
                                <expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan cert="unknown">H.</expan> Schöttleins, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>s</expan>, <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>. Der ist czü
                                <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> czeit niht anheim, aber wenn er her heim
                        kümt, so <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir in darumb
                            <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> cze rede <expan>secze<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        und ew ein <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>lasse<ex>n</ex></expan> wissen, ob <expan>yema<ex>n</ex>t</expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> czü uns kümt und die
                            <expan>vord<ex>er</ex>t</expan>. Wo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb und dinst
                            <expan>beweise<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>möht<ex>en</ex></expan>, das <expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                                <expan>allcz<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>uts<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
